Modified version of Putty that includes following fixes:

---------------------------------------------------------

alt + arrows correctly mapped
shift + arrows correctly mapped
ctrl + shift + arrows correctly mapped
alt + shift + arrows correctly mapped
ctrl + tab & ctrl + shift + tab correctly mapped
ctrl + click on link to open it browser

---------------------------------------------------------

Current version: r3
Provided as a patch file that must be applied to Putty 0.62 source for Windows
For already compiled version see Downloads

Created specially for emacs and vim console experience

Updated to latest Release 0.62

NOTE: This patch is included in the latest version of KiTTY http://www.9bis.net/kitty/
